Package: abmAME
Title: An R Package for Simulating Animal Movement Using an Agent-Based Model EXTENDED
Version: 0.1.3.0000
Date: 2023-11-07
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Margaret Elizabeth",
           family = "Swift",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "margaret.swift@cornell.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7913-1879")))
Description: The *abmAME* simulates animal movement use a discrete time agent-based model, programmed in C++ via the Rcpp package. The simulations include a number of key internal and external movement influences, as well as parameters for navigation and mobility capacity of the animal.
